                    <li>The lush and mountainous topography of the island is a paradise for hikers. There are a hundred options for tourists, whether to go on an easy trail or an intermediate one, or a challenging hike. Some of the best islands for hiking are Dominica, Jamaica, Martinique, Grenada, Saint Lucia, St Vincent, and many more. </li>
